ingredients.alim_nom_eng: Orange juice, reconstituted from a concentrate

ingredients_text: Sugar, cocoa mass, almonds 7%, cocoa butter, orange juice from concentrate 3.9%, anhydrous milk fat, invert sugar, lemon juice from concentrate, emulsifier (soya lecithin), pineapple, gelling agent (pectin), natural orange flavouring, artificial flavouring (vanillin).
